data.description: This stunning 5-bedroom residence boasts over 3500 square feet of living space and is the epitome of luxury and convenience. A home office/study, formal dining, and a spacious living area create a perfect blend of functionality and style. The kitchen, adorned with granite countertops, stainless gas cooktop, and a built-in oven with ample cabinet space. The primary bathroom offers double sinks, separate tub, a shower, and walk-in closet for ultimate relaxation. Upstairs enjoy a game room, four bedrooms, and two full bathrooms, providing plenty of space and comfort for your family. A covered back patio offers an ideal spot for outdoor relaxation. Effortlessly maintain the lush landscaping with a built-in sprinkler system. Situated on a corner lot in a peaceful cul-de-sac street, this home combines elegance with a prime location.
